defaultAbout the authordefaultGreg Powerdefault has been involved in political and parliamentary reform for around 20 years. He co-founded Global Partners in 2005 to deliver projects to strengthen representative politics
default, since working in countries in the Middle East, sub-Saharan Africa and Latin America
default.
