default&#xa0;
defaultHe has also provided advice to a variety of international organisations and donor agencies helping, amongst others, the Danish foreign ministry to establish their multi-party institute, and International IDEA to evaluate their work on political parties.
default 
default He writes widely on issues such as the application of political economy analysis, donor approaches to governance assistance, and parliamentary transparency. 
default 
defaultHe is the author of the first 
defaultGlobal Parliamentary Report
default, published by the UNDP and IPU in 2012.
